      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "OVERDRIVE (2) got the job done at Ascot two back before a 0.2L defeat in Saturday company before the break. She looks back in top order judging by her latest trial win around some handy types. Well placed from the barrier and can return on a winning note. LAST STYLEBENDER (1) led them up and scored a narrow win at Ascot first-up when jumping favourite. Up to a CL3 today, but the rating out of the fresh run was strong and he can improve again with that run under the belt. Nottle rides now and he can go on with the job. KING'S DRAMA (3) flew home to just miss behind  LAST STYLEBENDER last start. He'll be better for that run and he gets a nice weight swing in his favour today. Watch for him flying late in the race again. SCENIC GEORGE (4) is never far away and can make an impression once again. MANDIBLE MAGIC (5) was good in a much tougher race last start and comes back to midweek company today. Live chance.",
